ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Token
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
-- the parameters for the buttons used to control the token
buttonParams = {}
-- the ID of the previous Wait function
waitID = nil
-- the old value before it started to change
oldValue = nil

function onLoad(save_state)
    -- these units are in global positions unaffected by scale
    buttonParams = {
        {
            params = {
                click_function = "none",
                function_owner = self,
                label          = self.value,
                position       = vector(0, 0.1, 0),
                rotation       = vector(0, 0, 0),
                width          = 0,
                height         = 0,
                font_size      = 330
            },
            unique_function = function() end
        },
        {
            params = {
                click_function = "plusOne",
                function_owner = self,
                label          = "+",
                position       = vector(0.5, 0.1, -0.5),
                rotation       = vector(0, 0, 0),
                width          = 350,
                height         = 350,
                font_size      = 330
            },
            unique_function = function() change_value(1) end
        },
        {
            params = {
                click_function = "minusOne",
                function_owner = self,
                label          = "-",
                position       = vector(-0.5, 0.1, 0.5),
                rotation       = vector(0, 0, 0),
                width          = 350,
                height         = 350,
                font_size      = 330
            },
            unique_function = function() change_value(-1) end
        }
    }

    for _, v in ipairs(buttonParams) do
        if v.unique_function then
            self.setVar(v.params.click_function, v.unique_function)
        end
        local scaledParams = deepCopy(v.params)
        scaledParams.position = vector(
            scaledParams.position.x / self.getScale().x,
            scaledParams.position.y / self.getScale().y,
            scaledParams.position.z / self.getScale().z
        )
        scaledParams.width = scaledParams.width / self.getScale().x
        scaledParams.height = scaledParams.height / self.getScale().z
        scaledParams.font_size = scaledParams.font_size / self.getScale().z
        self.createButton(scaledParams)
    end
end

function change_value(amount)
    -- get the old value if we don't already have one
    oldValue = oldValue or self.value

    -- change the value and clamp it to be at least 0
    self.value = self.value + amount
    if self.value < 0 then self.value = 0 end

    -- update the display
    self.editButton({index = 0, label = self.value})

    local newValue = self.value
    function change_value_wait()
        if self.value > oldValue then
            printToAll(self.getDescription() .. " gained " .. self.value - oldValue .. " " .. self.getName())
        elseif self.value < oldValue then
            printToAll(self.getDescription() .. " lost " .. oldValue - self.value .. " " .. self.getName())
        end
        -- reset the old value
        oldValue = nil
        -- set the ID back to nil so we don't try to stop a function thats already been called
        waitID = nil
    end

    -- stop the previous waited function call
    if waitID ~= nil then
        Wait.stop(waitID)
    end
    -- printToAll the message after 3 seconds
    waitID = Wait.time(change_value_wait, 3)
end

function onDrop(player_color)
    for i, v in ipairs(buttonParams) do
        local scaledParams = {}
        scaledParams.index = i - 1
        scaledParams.position = vector(
            v.params.position.x / self.getScale().x,
            v.params.position.y / self.getScale().y,
            v.params.position.z / self.getScale().z
        )
        scaledParams.width = v.params.width / self.getScale().x
        scaledParams.height = v.params.height / self.getScale().z
        scaledParams.font_size = v.params.font_size / self.getScale().z
        self.editButton(scaledParams)
    end
end

function deepCopy(original)
    local copy = nil
    if type(original) == "table" then
        copy = {}
        for k, v in pairs(original) do
            copy[k] = deepCopy(v)
        end
    else
        copy = original
    end

    return copy
end
